---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "April 24, 2026";
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service - Upraizo"
  description="Upraizo Terms of Service. Read the rules, guidelines, and agreements for using our educational platform."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-900/30 border-b border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 rounded-t-3xl">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-black text-red-500 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Legal & Agreements</h2>
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 font-medium">
        Last updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="space-y-16 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium">
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing and using Upraizo (the "Platform"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our platform or purchase our courses. These terms apply to all visitors, users, and others who access or use the Service.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">2. User Accounts</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            When you create an account with us, you must provide information that is accurate, complete, and current at all times. Failure to do so constitutes a breach of the Terms, which may result in immediate termination of your account.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mt-4 list-disc pl-6">
            <li>You are responsible for safeguarding the password that you use to access the Service.</li>
            <li>You agree not to disclose your password to any third party.</li>
            <li><strong>Account sharing is strictly prohibited.</strong> Your account is for your personal use only.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">3. Course Access & License</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            When you purchase a course on Upraizo, you are granted a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable license to access and view the course content for your personal, non-commercial, educational purposes.
          </p>
          <p>
            You may not reproduce, redistribute, transmit, assign, sell, broadcast, rent, share, lend, modify, adapt, edit, create derivative works of, license, or otherwise transfer or use any course content unless we give you explicit permission to do so.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-950/20 border border-indigo-100 dark:border-indigo-900/30">
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-indigo-900 dark:text-indigo-100 mb-6 tracking-tight">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-indigo-800 dark:text-indigo-200">
            The Service and its original content (including all videos, text, graphics, logos, and course materials), features, and functionality are and will remain the exclusive property of Upraizo and its licensors. Our intellectual property may not be used in connection with any product or service without the prior written consent of Upraizo.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">5. Refunds & Cancellations</h2>
          <p>
            We stand behind the quality of our courses. If you are entirely unsatisfied with your purchase, please contact our support team. Refunds are granted on a case-by-case basis within the specific refund window clearly stated at the time of purchase. Once a refund is issued, your access to the course material will be revoked immediately.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">6. Termination</h2>
          <p>
            We may terminate or suspend your account and bar access to the Service immediately, without prior notice or liability, under our sole discretion, for any reason whatsoever and without limitation, including but not limited to a breach of the Terms (e.g., sharing account credentials, pirating content).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">7. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right, at our sole discretion, to modify or replace these Terms at any time. By continuing to access or use our Service after any revisions become effective, you agree to be bound by the revised terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">8. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:support@upraizo.com" class="inline-flex mt-6 px-8 py-4 bg-zinc-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-zinc-900 font-bold rounded-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
            support@upraizo.com
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
